metadata.name: Genesis Stream “Marry Another Man” DreamGAN Live #2
metadata.description: Collect a piece of Wise John's creative process during his first even livestream on Koop.xyz. You’ll see how the video creation process works, and in the downtime while the scenes are rendering, he’ll play you some songs, do little AMA’s, and answer any questions you might have about the process.. After the event, the recording of the stream will be uploaded and attached to the metadata of this token.
